    {
      "id": "p003",
      "index": 3,
      "source": "However, if the GEMM Epilogue consumes SMEM, there is less available for the main loop and so the stage count used must be lower. Here, we use an epilogue that consumes no SMEM, and therefore the lines end along the X-axis when the total SMEM consumed by stage buffers reaches the max SMEM capacity per-SM.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0150",
      "parent_block_index": 150,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "However, if the GEMM Epilogue consumes SMEM, there is less available for the main loop and so the stage count used must be lower. Here, we use an epilogue that consumes no SMEM, and therefore the lines end along the X-axis when the total SMEM consumed by stage buffers reaches the max SMEM capacity per-SM.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "However, if the GEMM Epilogue consumes SMEM, there is less available for the main loop and so the stage count used must be lower. Here, we use an epilogue that consumes no SMEM, and therefore the lines end along the X-axis when the total SMEM consumed by stage buffers reaches the max SMEM capacity per-SM.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 306,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "然而，如果 GEMM 的 Epilogue（收尾操作）消耗了共享内存 (SMEM)，主循环可用的容量就会减少，因此必须降低使用的阶段数。在这里，我们使用不消耗共享内存 (SMEM) 的 Epilogue，因此，当阶段缓冲区消耗的总共享内存 (SMEM) 达到每个 SM 的最大容量时，曲线会在 X 轴方向上终止。",
          "model": "pro",
